Recommends: dosfstools,
            xfsprogs,
            e2fsprogs,
            libguestfs-tools
Suggests: confidential-data-hub,
          attestation-agent
Description: Full-disk encryption tooling for system volumes
 Cryptpilot-fde provides system disk encryption and boot-time processing
 for full-disk encryption setups. Includes cryptpilot-convert for disk
 image conversion and cryptpilot-enhance for FDE enhancement.

Package: cryptpilot-crypt
Architecture: any
Depends: cryptsetup-bin,
         coreutils,
